query:
-- Finde das Template SP-2026-003
SELECT id, uniqueId, title, isPublic FROM taskTemplates WHERE uniqueId LIKE '%SP-2026-003%' OR uniqueId LIKE '%2026-003%';

-- Zeige alle organizationTemplates für Organization 330025
SELECT ot.*, tt.uniqueId, tt.title 
FROM organizationTemplates ot 
LEFT JOIN taskTemplates tt ON ot.templateId = tt.id 
WHERE ot.organizationId = 330025;
